txt.en: Now that you have seen what lies inside Shathur-munzu, you feel it is your responsibility to deal with the warg threat as much as you are able. You should defeat as many wargs as possible in the wilds of Duskenvale and Shathur-munzu.
You have discovered that Shathur-munzu is the den of the Wargs of the Vales, and feel you must do what you can to rid the land of this threat.
Duskenvale has become a haven of the foul Wargs of the Vales.\n\nYou should defeat wargs in Duskenvale and Shathur-munzu.
You have done much to cleanse Duskenvale of the warg menace. The people of the Vales are safer for your actions.
